<item>
            <title>[FLINK-5071] YARN: yarn.containers.vcores config not respected when checking for vcores</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-5071</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The YarnClient validates whether the number of task slots is less then the max vcores settings of yarn but seems to ignore the yarn.containers.vcores flink config which should be used instead of the slots.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13020813">FLINK-5071</key>
            <summary>YARN: yarn.containers.vcores config not respected when checking for vcores</summary>
